s the general reader who enjoys her writing. This is the first significant book-length critical evaluation in ten years.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aLiterature Studies 2020. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aDoris Lessing.  aGolden Notebook.  aNobel Prize.  aempire.  afeminism.  agender.  anation.  anovelist.  apostcolonial theory.  arace.1 aWatkins, Susan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978184779354640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781847793546423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781847793546/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles